<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1361610" n="1"/>
    <opener><lb/>Viro <abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> et <abbr>Celeberr.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> 
        <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs> 
        <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-102552517">Petrus Antonius Michelotti</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> </opener>
    <p><lb/>Spero quod meas <rs type="letter" key="B_1720-03-02_991170517025805501">litteras</rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>a dato</expan></choice> <date when="1720-03-02">2 huius mensis</date> datas
        <lb/>atque per <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2775220">Oenipont<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> missas jam acceperis. Placet
        <lb/>ad Te scribere hac die via <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2950159">Bergomi</rs>, rursusque
    <lb/>rogare ut quam primum fieri poterit remittas me<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
        <lb/><rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">Dissertationem</rs> correct<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> ab Inclyto <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruo</rs> Tuo, cui salu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tem plurimam mitto. Si via <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2950159">Bergomi</rs> est tuta, vel
        <lb/>etiam tutior quam via <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3173435">Mediolani</rs> poteris mittere
        <lb/>fascicul<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2950159">Bergomum</rs> cum hac inscriptione
        <lb/>All'<abbr>Ill.ma</abbr> <abbr>Sig.<hi rend="sup">ra</hi></abbr> <abbr>Sig.<hi rend="sup">ra</hi></abbr> <abbr>P.na</abbr> mia <abbr>Coll.ma</abbr> la <abbr>sig.<hi rend="sup">ra</hi></abbr>
        <lb/>Contessa <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1326330934">Vertova Colleoni</rs><choice><orig>.</orig><reg>,</reg></choice> <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2950159">Bergamo</rs>. Nam h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c
        <lb/>Comitissa accipiet <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">fascicul<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>, et statim eum
        <lb/>ad me transmittet. Sed si via <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3173435">Mediolani</rs> est com<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>modior, celerior, et tutior, poteris (ut in alia <rs type="letter" key="B_1720-03-02_991170517025805501">epistola</rs> 
    <lb/>rogavi) mittere ad aliqu<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> <rs type="person">Mercator<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice></rs> indicando
    <lb/>mihi antequ<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> mittas, vel statim ac miseris
        <lb/>nomen et cognomen <rs type="person">mercatoris</rs> ut possit
        <lb/>ad illum <rs type="person">Mercator<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice></rs> scribere Marchio <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1221327275">Butin<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>trochi</rs>. Negoti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> tot<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> tuo amori, et tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> prudenti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
    <lb/>commendo. Ceterum spero Te bene valere uti
        <lb/>etiam <abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup"><choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></hi></abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patru<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>, qui credo sciet, <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1055365613">Jacob<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
            <lb/>Keilliu<subst><del><gap/></del><add>m</add></subst></rs>, de quo dico in mea <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">Dissertatione</rs>, esse mor<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tu<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>. Roga meo nomine ips<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup"><choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></hi></abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patru<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>
    <lb/>ut respondeat ad argument<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, quo aliqui utun<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tur ad convellend<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> opinionem quam ipsemmet
        <lb/>et <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118571249">Leibnitius</rs>, <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-129832952">Connoro</rs> Anglo Duce, tenet de <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_8VCJJVI7">Secretio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>
    <pb facs="1361611" n="2"/>
            <lb/>ne Liquor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> in Animantibus</rs>. Argument<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> est hujus<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>modi. Animali non bene valente excernuntur ex
    <lb/>Glandulis, verbi causa, renalibus Humores pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tern<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>aturales nullam<del> fere</del> similitudinem cum Urina
    <lb/>habentes: tales autem Humores pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ternaturales
    <lb/>verrant cavitates Glandular<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> renalium, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ser<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tim morbo diu durante, ita ut in ejusmodi Glan<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dular<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> cavitatibus nihil Urin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> remaneat. <choice><orig><g ref="#AE">Æ</g></orig><reg>Ae</reg></choice>gro
    <lb/>autem convalescente vel Arte, vel Natura Urina
    <lb/>adhuc separatur in renalibus Glandulis. Tunc igitur 
    <lb/>separatur sive Urina pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>existente in comme<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>moratar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Glandular<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> cavitatibus, quas Urina
    <lb/>esse imbutas ab initio generationis <subst><del>ponit</del><add>posuerunt</add></subst>
        <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruus</rs>, <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118571249">Leibnitius</rs> post <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-129832952">Connorum</rs>, aliosque.
    <lb/>Deinde <add>et</add> Humores isti pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ternaturales naturalibus
    <lb/>dissimiles separantur in Glandulis sive pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>viis
        <lb/>sive pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>existentibus Humoribus pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ternaturalibus
        <lb/>sibi similibus. Fiunt ergo separationes in Ani<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mantibus Liquorum pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ternaturali<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> licet Glandul<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
        <lb/>non sint imbut<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, et veluti antea madefact<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Humo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ribus pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ternaturalibus.</p>
    <p><lb/>Versus fin<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">Dissertationis</rs> commemorabo <abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">i</hi></abbr>
        <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patrui</rs>, <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118571249">Leibnitii</rs>, et <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-129832952">Connori</rs> Sententi<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_8VCJJVI7">de secretione
            <lb/>Animali</rs>, quamobrem rogo ut allat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> objectioni
        <pb facs="1361613" n="3"/>
<lb/>dignetur occurrere.</p> <closer><salute>Vale Vir Amicissime</salute>, et me amare
    <dateline><lb/>perge. Dab<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> <rs type="place" key="place_VER-repven">Venetiis</rs> <date when="1720-03-10"><choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>a dato</expan></choice> 10 Martii 1720</date><supplied>.</supplied></dateline>
    <pb facs="1361614" n="4"/>
    <address><addrLine>A Monsieur</addrLine> 
        <addrLine>Monsieur Nicolas Bernoulli</addrLine>
        <addrLine>Professeur tres Celebre de Mathematique</addrLine>
        <addrLine>franca per Bergamo</addrLine>
        <addrLine><choice><orig>a</orig><reg>à</reg></choice> <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661604">Basle</rs></addrLine></address></closer>
</div>
